
Project Goals 
Simple Rules engine (RE).   
1. Given input video, create rule/DAG for pre-ingest processes and upon success, 
complete the ingest move to asset bucket, and add to asset table.. 
2. Given successful ingest, use inspection details to create rule/DAG for transcoding, and 
on successful encode, move output(s) to the encoded video bucket, and create record. 
3. Create unit tests to verify the implementation. 
Key Points: 
● Initial version will only consider a single ingest inspection, 
and a single model for encoding. 
● The execution engine is not in the initial scope of this project for contractor.  
Company will own that work. 
● All table schemas will be jointly defined by contractor and company.